<title>USA: Ansoft acquires Compact Software.</title>
<headline>Ansoft acquires Compact Software.</headline>
<dateline>PITTSBURGH 1997-04-09</dateline>
<text>
<p>Ansoft Corp said on Wednesday that it has acquired Compact Software Inc, a privately held corporation, for 1.3 million shares of common stock and $3 million in cash.</p>
<p>Ansoft said it will post a one-time charge in the fourth quarter of the year ending April 30, 1997, to cover merger costs.</p>
<p>&quot;The addition of Compact is expected to have a significant positive impact on revenues and profits in the upcoming and future fiscal years,&quot; Ansoft said in a statement.  </p>
<p>Ansoft said the deal is valued at approximately $10.0 million.</p>
